Youtube AD Skipper is the extension helps you to automatically skip Youtube ads as they appear.

You often watch Youtube and are bothered by ads, you have to manually skip them? Now that is no longer a problem, Youtube AD Skipper will do it for you.

P.S. We will never collect or sell your data.
